                    </div>
                    <span>If you write web applications and are serious about their security, you need this book. The book gets you inside the mind of a hacker and shows you why simply having the latest patches and security updates is not enough.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Good read for (beginner-mid-level) security professionals</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>4</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>0</span>
                      /
                      <span>0</span>
